POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User"
}

### Test 2: Duplicate Email (409)
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com"
